Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:11.75,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜落！！！月夜的片倉君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:19.91,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒人趁著夜色逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:48.17,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:53.48,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:03.51,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:11.85,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶可沒見過這種作物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:24.43,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:36.03,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:52.33,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:57.03,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 龍之右目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:00.47,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼你在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:03.32,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道這裡是伊達的領地嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:05.25,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.94,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被委託照顧夢吉 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:11.01,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正用武田的飛行忍具回越後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:13.58,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在路上…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.15,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍具爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:18.47,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是悲劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:24.47,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過掉在這裡也算是不幸中的萬幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:30.34,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的禮物我很感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:33.53,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得這樣飛不起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.90,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年收成不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:41.93,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請轉告軍神 這是上次欠他的情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.27,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:46.75,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢吉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:05.43,chunri,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不行啊 混蛋 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:08.08,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無需多慮！我來助你！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:23.29,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趁新鮮送到哦
